sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant WebUI as Angular UI
    participant AgentService as Agent Service
    participant NATS as NATS JetStream
    participant ControlPlane as Control Plane
    participant CrewAIContainer as CrewAI Container
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: CrewAI Service-Level Flow

    User->>WebUI: Start chat with CrewAI project
    WebUI->>AgentService: POST /api/chatkit<br/>{message, agent_type: "crewai", folder}
    AgentService->>PostgreSQL: Create thread
    PostgreSQL-->>AgentService: Thread created

    Note over AgentService,NATS: Container Creation
    AgentService->>NATS: Publish agent.control.{run_id}.start<br/>{run_id, user_id, task, folder, ...}
    NATS-->>AgentService: Published

    NATS->>ControlPlane: Deliver start message
    ControlPlane->>CrewAIContainer: Create container with env vars<br/>(RUN_ID, USER_ID, FOLDER, NATS_URL, etc.)
    ControlPlane->>PostgreSQL: Save ChatContainer record
    ControlPlane-->>NATS: ACK

    Note over CrewAIContainer,NATS: Worker Bootstrap
    CrewAIContainer->>CrewAIContainer: Start CrewAI worker process
    CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Connect to NATS
    CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Ensure streams<br/>(AGENT_CHAT, AGENT_CONTROL, AGENT_EVENTS)
    CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Subscribe to user events<br/>agent.user.{uid}.chat.{rid}.user.events
    CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Subscribe to control close<br/>agent.control.{run_id}.close
    CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish ready signal<br/>agent.control.worker.{run_id}.ready
    NATS-->>CrewAIContainer: ACK

    NATS->>AgentService: Ready signal received
    AgentService-->>WebUI: SSE: Worker ready
    WebUI-->>User: Display worker ready

    Note over CrewAIContainer,NATS: Project Resolution
    alt Runnable folder found
        CrewAIContainer->>CrewAIContainer: Detect command & start process
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish state "started"<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.started
    else No runnable folder - scan for projects
        CrewAIContainer->>CrewAIContainer: Scan workspace for CrewAI projects
        alt Projects found
            CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish chat final<br/>status: "project_selection_required"
            NATS->>AgentService: Chat event
            AgentService-->>WebUI: SSE: Show project selection UI
            User->>WebUI: Select project
            WebUI->>AgentService: POST /api/chatkit<br/>{selected_project}
            AgentService->>NATS: Publish agent.control.{run_id}.resume<br/>{folder: selected_project}
            NATS->>ControlPlane: Resume message
            ControlPlane->>CrewAIContainer: Recreate container with new folder
            CrewAIContainer->>CrewAIContainer: Restart with selected project
        else No projects found
            CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish state "failed"
            CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish chat final<br/>status: "failed"
        end
    end

    Note over CrewAIContainer,WebUI: Output Streaming
    loop Process output
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish state "output"<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.output
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish chat "progress_update"<br/>agent.user.{uid}.chat.{rid}.worker.events
        NATS->>AgentService: Events received
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE events
        WebUI->>User: Display output
    end

    Note over CrewAIContainer,WebUI: Input Prompt Handling
    alt Input prompt detected
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish state "waiting_input"<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.waiting_input
        NATS->>AgentService: Waiting input event
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE: Show input dialog
        User->>WebUI: Enter input
        WebUI->>AgentService: POST /api/chatkit/input/{run_id}
        AgentService->>NATS: Publish user event<br/>agent.user.{uid}.chat.{rid}.user.events
        NATS->>CrewAIContainer: User input received
        CrewAIContainer->>CrewAIContainer: Send input to process
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish state "output" (stdin echo)
    end

    Note over CrewAIContainer,WebUI: Process Completion
    alt Exit code == 0
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish state "completed"<br/>agent.user.{uid}.events.{rid}.state.completed
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish chat "final_answer"<br/>status: "completed"
        NATS->>AgentService: Completed event
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE final event
        WebUI->>User: Show "CrewAI run completed"
    else Exit code != 0
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish state "failed"
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish chat "final_answer"<br/>status: "failed"
        NATS->>AgentService: Failed event
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE error
        WebUI->>User: Show "CrewAI run failed"
    end

    Note over User,CrewAIContainer: Cancellation
    alt User closes chat
        User->>WebUI: Close chat
        WebUI->>AgentService: POST /api/chatkit/close/{run_id}
        AgentService->>NATS: Publish agent.control.{run_id}.close
        NATS->>ControlPlane: Close message
        NATS->>CrewAIContainer: Control close received
        CrewAIContainer->>CrewAIContainer: Graceful shutdown
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish state "cancelled"
        CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Publish chat "final_answer"<br/>status: "cancelled"
        NATS->>AgentService: Cancelled event
        AgentService->>WebUI: SSE cancelled
        ControlPlane->>CrewAIContainer: Stop and remove container
        ControlPlane->>PostgreSQL: Update ChatContainer status
    end

    Note over CrewAIContainer,NATS: Worker Cleanup
    CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Unsubscribe from topics
    CrewAIContainer->>NATS: Close connection
    NATS-->>CrewAIContainer: Disconnected
